{"type": "article", "id": 30911, "title": "想听黑胶？你可以自己动手做一个唱片机｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-08-11T23:12:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 31409, "name": "Spinbox"}, {"id": 31410, "name": "Almleuchten"}, {"id": 31411, "name": "WEND Studio"}, {"id": 31412, "name": "Pawena Studio"}, {"id": 27455, "name": "Bryan Wong"}, {"id": 31413, "name": "Pawena Thimaporn"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 253, "image": "img/article/article_show/201608120006404aFQ1RceDy9muoLg.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Spinbox by Spinbox Team</h3><p>动辄上万元的高价和复杂的设备是不是让你对黑胶唱片望之却步？来自台湾的设计团队抱着“人人有胶听”的梦想，推出了一款自行组装的 DIY 黑胶唱片机 Spinbox。当你收到 Spinbox 时，装有组件的外盒其实就是机器本体，只需要按照说明书的提示就可以很轻松地完成组装。Spinbox 所采用的纸盒不仅外型时尚，经过特殊上膜后还拥有了防潮的功能，坚固耐用。顶端设计的把手可以让你将它带在身边，与朋友分享黑胶唱片的独特魅力。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.zeczec.com/projects/spinbox\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 2980 新台币。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812000748gJFpIxNqnB47ek0v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.475000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812000751sYdB0gfLTIJPDWle.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812000749EpQqvB1G7eDznRPc.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812000748L4gRGDu6aF1ZrYfQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.044386\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812000748oeM7BGcF2w85KZNX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812000748vGB3xeX8PSR1AbW7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Almleuchten by Felix Fehr &amp; Harald Hofer</h3><p>奥地利独立灯具品牌 Almleuchten 由 Felix Fehr 和 Harald Hofer 共同创立，从木料的裂痕和纹路中透露出的沧桑感赋予了灯具一种天然的魅力。Almleuchten 所使用的大部分木料均取自蒂罗尔（Tyrol）当地高山上废弃的木屋，因此每一盏灯都是独一无二的。得益于特殊的切割工艺，灯具在点亮后还会散发出温暖的红光。如果你对它们感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"http://www.almleuchten.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方网站</a>进行订购。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812000835MNXdOmcCt904Bvnf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.698333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812000835gd6j5vRObqQkHf2w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608120008359A7ua3le5rQUWkgZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812000835TfFdH3Qeo8ku7W5p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812000835xvH9TnJSfgDeVUOI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812000835N1pqBGWDsiLo8gln.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Handwoven Rattan Chairs by WEND Studio</h3><p>美国加州的 <a href=\"http://wend-studio.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">WEND Studio</a> 最近与印尼爪哇岛上的编织匠展开合作，将现代的设计风格与传统工艺结合在一起，推出了一系列手工编织的藤椅。半开放式椅背由各种重叠的线条构成，带给人一种独特的视觉效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812000908xSWFH0InYskhu4Tp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812000908rfTBpbzqROY1gvan.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.670000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812000908Kq4Lrdg5DuznhoQx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812000908ByPFbSuaEsNpd2A1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812000909C1vl6ek0tVufySId.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.070000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608120009087qyon9k04dJR8SpL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.670000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Aluminum Heatsink Laptop Stand by Bryan Wong</h3><p>当你选对了材料，笔记本支架可以做得既好看又实用，Bryan Wong 设计的这款铝制支架就是一个典型的例子。它的造型非常精简，仅利用金属本身的特质和高低不平的栅格形底部进行散热。如果你对这个支架感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"http://www.bryanwongdesign.com/#/aluminum-heatsink-laptop-stand/\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>与设计师联系。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608120009425ymFK3e6Obtvdhck.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664773\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812000942lxPK38iOgRrkeadv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664773\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812000938pGJi5whSHF3Vo4ld.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664773\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608120009402ZJtKHM1pzdyOEWo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664773\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812000942CQDc7xtul1mSHReO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664773\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812000942flvWFSU5Ct2NYADJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664773\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Symphonica by Symphonica Team</h3><p>看腻了市面上千篇一律的 iPhone 扬声器，这个名为 <a href=\"http://www.symphonicasound.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Symphonica</a> 的不插电木制“小喇叭”或许会带给你一种质朴而复古的感觉。它的内部是经过特殊设计的声学腔体结构，能够在没有电路的影响下做到对音质的高度还原。考虑到续航问题，设计师还为 Symphonica 添加了隐藏式的充电线接口，使用时只要将线穿过、插入手机即可。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/symphonica/symphonica\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 75 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812001002MvH31qlZzTRW9yDC.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669118\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812001001P0ozbqsX7ASK9lVZ.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669118\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812001001gqeJcy47d5Qo39NX.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669118\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812001002wrA3UlVgYGBHdiDL.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.672059\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016081200100117WySXjfUtLP5GJ8.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.547059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Nana Family by Pawena Studio</h3><p>洛杉矶的 Pawena Studio 是一间专注于手工陶器的工作室，除了几何图案的纹样之外，设计师 Pawena Thimaporn 还推出了以人物为主题的 nana 系列。由一家三口组成的陶器套装不仅可以用作餐具，也很适合放上空气凤梨或是多肉植物。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.pawenastudio.com/shop/a-family-of-three-set-of-6-bowls-and-cups\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，整套售价为 180 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812001029giB6Ocufyo3YhADN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812001033xOHVDzBvY5Nu7UEk.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812001032LicSFMvXmrgqTEU9.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.652667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812001030GJsPgK1qWEb7dZLM.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812001032rE0C2yGwuBbLOdqI.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160812001032N42csQquPFtHLJ5M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.654000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div>"}